So another example of an attribute is actually I belief width.

00:03:23.835 --> 00:03:32.725
So let's try changing the width of that image to make it only 55 percent.

00:03:32.724 --> 00:03:36.310
Now, you can see we have a much smaller image.

00:03:36.310 --> 00:03:39.330
So here, it's an image element,

00:03:39.330 --> 00:03:41.295
we use an IMG tag.

00:03:41.294 --> 00:03:45.189
The attributes that we added were the source which is where the image is

00:03:45.189 --> 00:03:49.389
coming from and the width which is the size that we want the image to be.

